Title: Doraemon: Nobita's Art World Tales
Actors: Wasabi Mizuta, Megumi Ôhara, Yumi Kakazu
Plot: Set in the magnificent world of medieval Europe depicted in paintings. Doraemon and his friends jump into the "world of the painting" joined by Claire and her friends Milo and Chai as they emabark on a great adventure!.
